                      <font face="arial" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> I startede my necro back in 1999 when EQ came out, and have since day 1 loved to play him. All you guys who started at that time too, knows about all the changes we have been through, i mean at that time our lvl 49 pet could kill a full equipt warrior.<br /><br />This post is not a post to compare Necros vs others classes, this post is about why Varant has to make some big stupids nerfs. Over the years varant have made so many non-creative nerfs, and i must admit that its seems like their world is eíther black or white ???? there are simply no "grey" areas.<br /><br />But enough of the history, this is simply about yesterdays nerf. Its simply so Not-understandble, both in a cormercial point of wiew and in an gaming point of wiew. <br /><br />Its very true that the charm exping in CoD have been overpowered, we all knew that, but then again - in the last 3-4 years i have been playing, then the last 2 weeks in cod have been some of the most funny non raiding time i have had in Everquest. But we all knew that a nerf was incomming.<br /><br />But what a nerf. As all my fellow necromancers say, we could have lived with the exp nerf on 30%, i would even had said 50%, because personaly i was not only doing charm exp in CoD because of AA exp, but because it was so entertaining, i mean the adrenalin was pumping in my veins all the time, when you had a lvl 61-70% hasted  warrior pet running next to you all the time when he was not beating all the other Currupted knights or deadh Knights up. And just for the record for all the necromancers that is never gonna have this expireince (cause of the Nerf) i have never died so many times in 1 zone before as i have in CoD, so its very true to say, that even tho that the Exp was very good - the risk was also very high, but that was also a very fun part.<br /><br />SO..... i cant simply not understand why Sony want to take this part of the game away from us, and it is very true that charm exping in CoD is useless now, i tried my self after patch to see how the new ser***stances was in CoD, and i can only say what all others say.<br /><br />Resists like hell, but what is more annoying is that when i was so lucky to land a charm, then it broke after 10 sec. SO the conclution is CoD is a waste of time. So i gues its back to Agrokiting.... oh no than have been nerfed to.. **** then its back to fearkiting....oh no that has been nerfed too... so what is left for the best or used to best solo class in EQ - ohh its root-cooking, so welcome to the land of wannabe Druids.<br /><br />Sometimes it would be really nice if we could get some explonations from sony about why they nerf as they do.<br /><br />I know that overall we are still a very strong class, just read some of Yag`s solo posts (my hero) but this is NOT dayli life in Everquest, this is just important sunshine stories.<br /><br />So now its back to boring root soloing or if we are lucky we can get a grp somewhere. Another fun part of the highend game have been taken away. And after reading some of you guys other posts it seems like its not only WoT that have been nerfed but also the other lvl 50-60 charms. <br /><br />We had 1 and only 1 zone in PoP where we could charm solo, but i guess that was 1 to much, so they had to take it away.<br /><br />Finally, i would like to say to all of you guys who dident try CoD-charm when it was possible, its a **** shame that you will never try this because it was a so fun-scary-entertaining experience.<br /><br />I know this sound like a big whinning post, but my point is that is so non-understandble for me how a dev team can be so non-creative, i simply dont get it.<br /><br />And for all you guys who gain lvl 65, DONT BUY Word of Terris.<br /><br />NB. well it was nice to get some anger of my chest, and sorry for the spelling.<br /><br />Have a nice day<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Taxa<br />Arch Lich